Application Programming Interfaces APIs
=======================================

+ It allows communication between two pieces of Softwares.
+ REST APIs are another type of API
+ Representational State Transfer APIs.
+ Allows you to Communicate through the Internet.
+ Enable you to use Resources like Storage, data and AI algorithms.

Working of REST APIs
====================

+ Used to Interact with Web Services.
+ Here a Set of Rule Regarding.
    + Communication
    + Input or Request - Client
    + Output or Response - Resources.
    + Request contain HTTP JSON content
    + Response contain HTTP JSON as response.
